<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.1.9">
<l>kūṭi yāṭiyu raitta tēyurait tāyeṉ neñcamaṉ pāytu ṇintukēḷ</l>
<l>pāṭi yāṭi<supplied>p</supplied>pa larumpa ṇintēttik kāṇkilār</l>
<l>āṭu tāmarai yōṉu mīcaṉu mamarar kōṉuniṉ</l>
<l>ṟēttum vēṅkaṭat</l>
<l>tāṭu kūttaṉuk kiṉṟa ṭimaittoḻil pūṇṭāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My companion heart, you have said what [others] said,</l>
<l rend="indent">joining and cavorting [together]; listen carefully.</l>
<l>Many, having sung, danced, bowed, and prayed, are not able to see [the lord].</l>
<l>Today you assumed the duty of service to the performer</l>
<l rend="indent">who dances on Vēṅkaṭam</l>
<l>Where the one on the swaying lotus, Īśa,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the king of the immortals continually worship.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
